summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting a Franchise from King County to construct, maintain and operate watermain pipelines on portions of 148th Avenue Southeast, Southeast 200th Street, Southeast Lake Youngs Way, Southeast 208th Street and South 208th Street, as therein more particularly set forth, for the Cedar River Pipeline No. 5, Phase I, watermain project, and authorizing and directing the Superintendent of Water to sign said Franchise for and on behalf of said City.
